Package net.jxta.ext.config

Interface Summary
IPAddressProfiler An interface which defines a standard way to evaluate a peers available IP addresses.
 

Class Summary
Address Address container.
Configurator A JXTA configurator.

Configurator serves primarily as a JXTA property sheet and implements very little attribute association logic beyond that of what is required to perform integrity validation and address expansion.
